  "keyFeatures": [
    "Creates SNS topic and Lambda function for Slack notifications",
    "Supports AWS CloudWatch Alarms with color-coded severity",
    "Handles GuardDuty findings and malware scan results",
    "Integrates with AWS Security Hub findings",
    "Supports AWS Health Events and AWS Backup notifications",
    "KMS encryption support for Slack webhook URL",
    "VPC deployment support for Lambda function",
    "Custom Lambda function override capability",
    "SNS topic delivery status logging",
    "Python 3.13 Lambda runtime"
